90</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">連登TSV表格</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1-nLEhICVWVioxn7qmzzkWAGYmGw_4sZgY08PTEFgQMQ/edit#gid=1946986237\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1-nLEhICVWVioxn7qmzzkWAGYmGw_4sZgY08PTEFgQMQ%2Fedit%23gid%3D1946986237&d=y8GnNjpPWm%2BETVwSsq17pxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=df7f2ae9\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1-nLEhICVWVioxn7qmzzkWAGYmGw_4sZgY08PTEFgQMQ/edit#gid=1946986237</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><ins>常見問題</ins></span></strong></span><br />\n努力值點樣練先最快？<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">病毒努力值*2, 出現連鎖後所有*2, 狗帶+8<br />\n打1場連鎖7隻[(1+8)*2*2*7 = 252]<br />\nHP: 弱丁魚[+1]/保姆曼波[+2] (水試練最入氣泡釣魚100%)<br />\nA: 家門雀/貓鼬少 (屋企右邊1號道路)<br />\nB: 屎眼石 (博士左手邊山洞)<br />\nC: 傻鴨 (2島水試練第1個草叢)<br />\nD: 大眼水母 (1島商業區對出海面)<br />\nS: 小哥達 (普試練地上黑影撞埋去)</span><br />\n<br />\n上面講既ABCDS係乜黎？<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">物攻/物防/特攻/特防/速度</span><br />\n<br />\n點睇我連唔到上網同人交換/對戰？<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">係咪未更新遊戲？ 現時版本<span style=\"color: red;\">V1.1</span><br />\n可以喺入GAME標題畫面右下角見到</span><br />\n<br />\n上咗網啦，點樣同朋友交換對戰？<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">要先喺3DS主畫面上方笑笑口公仔<span style=\"color: red;\">互相</span>輸入對方FC加好友<br />\n然後就會喺圓慶廣場下畫面對戰/交換入面見到自己朋友</span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請支持官方授權<br />\n香港Pok&eacute;mon比賽</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://playpokemonhk.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplaypokemonhk.com%2F&d=y8GnNjpPWm%2BETVwSsq17pxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=d635ac2b\" target=\"_blank\">http://playpokemonhk.com/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/PlayPokemonHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPlayPokemonHK%2F&d=y8GnNjpPWm%2BETVwS